Reasoning: The paper discusses the dynamics of the world publication system and uses analytical variants of the Web-of-Science to study the top-1% and top-10% most frequently cited publications. This suggests that the paper may fall under the categories of digital libraries (cs.DL), social and information networks (cs.SI), statistics (cs.ST), systems and control (cs.SY), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
